 The Website: A Self-Proclaimed AI Enthusiast's Playground\n\nThis website appears to be the personal playground of Edward Donner, a self-proclaimed AI enthusiast and co-founder of Nebula.io. On one hand, he enthusiastically shares his love for LLMs (Large Language Models), amateur electronic music production, and discussing AI-related topics with anyone who will listen. He's also proud to have created best-selling Udemy courses on these topics.\n\nOn the other hand, news-wise? Not much. A few old blog posts announcing new resources, like an AI Coder track and an n8n AI Builder, but no recent updates or announcements within the site itself. Guess this is more of a personal ramblings hub than a comprehensive resource for AI-related news...